{"tid":956920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"活烤非洲豬瘟　豬群被活活燒死發出淒厲慘叫","createTime":"2018-12-26T16:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T01:30:08.000Z","uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"38277102b605c2908bf18a8d6604649ffc843756","tid":956920,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181225/1489275/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181225%2F1489275%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=juzR4FIUJrY%2BQrCnrv7L7G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=360cdb81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181225%2F1489275%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=e0ca4e12\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181225/1489275/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n非洲豬瘟在中國失控蔓延，早前才剛有網友拍下，福建尤溪縣有上萬隻豬吐血倒地、屍疊屍，近日也有網友拍到，當局把疑似發病的活豬全丟進深坑，然後再扔下火種，把牠們活活烤死。期間，活豬們被火燒到在坑內不斷狂奔亂跳，發出淒厲的慘叫聲，令人慘不忍睹。<br />\n <br />\n公開影片的中國網友，沒有說明拍攝的地點與時間，但從影片可見，多隻活豬被扔進一個深達十多公尺的大坑內，坑內鋪滿稻草等易燃物。隨後，有人把火種丟入坑中，火種最初擊中一頭活豬，該豬因為受不了焚燒的劇痛，開始在坑內四處亂竄，結果令其他豬也全被點燃。最後，活豬們由於無路可逃，只能伴隨著淒厲的慘叫聲中，被活活燒死。火勢變小後，可以見到牠們的豬身都被熏黑，部分已動彈不得。<br />\n<br />\n中國於今年8月傳出非洲豬瘟疫情後，至今已經有23個省、市爆發疫情，尚未傳出疫情的地區僅剩：河北、山東、廣西、海南、寧夏、甘肅、新疆、西藏等8個省。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"eb2cf680491402773395dcadd20fe7efa6946884","tid":956920,"uid":39550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db2ea4519d396c5de545953676c9ddfc07a0d28","tid":956920,"uid":154106,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:36:47.000Z","msg":"支那人會有報應<br />\n豬豬這麼可愛怎可以殺豬豬"},{"pid":"83facc5bd42a879021a31848bcc354761531dc2c","tid":956920,"uid":69886,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"大愛撚準備全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399f06d99b218469af7b376b24aedaa08d74cd33","tid":956920,"uid":17232,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"83facc5bd42a879021a31848bcc354761531dc2c","tid":956920,"uid":69886,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"大愛撚準備全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"屌活燒豬都係大愛 你無撚野吓話？"},{"pid":"9e385f19d28aa6bcaf6ac9cf0ad87626e656241f","tid":956920,"uid":22422,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"中國人永遠都係埋哂啲問題入土<br />\n睇唔到就當冇事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講人唔人道嘅問題<br />\n同支那講人道主義嘥氣"},{"pid":"55b2f749410aa49c48d3b776315b68aa28f311e4","tid":956920,"uid":78791,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d95e3d0db00c13803980a9d857e38bd3c949c9f7","tid":956920,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:42:30.000Z","msg":"屌 睇完個心好撚唔舒服"},{"pid":"0b4d5858d4e38e12488e614d2cff418b16a31b6e","tid":956920,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"無睇片，但係咪無錢買電槍?"},{"pid":"2db5bc76fcf997c18cecc864f17886f5f1890457","tid":956920,"uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"loop登果然冇改錯名<br />\n樓主回帶都算，啲回復又係好似冇睇過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d89112429f9613745543316bbf4956bfe